LOCUS       PA1_O4_O3                 56 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  A 56-bp synthetic constitutive/IPTG-regulatable promoter combining
            the phage T7 A1 (PA1) core with two natural lac O1 operators placed
            at positions 4 (spacer) and 3 (downstream)..
